{"tid":569931,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗圖書館自修室真係傳播疾病嘅溫床","createTime":"2018-02-23T07:18:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-24T06:21:11.000Z","uid":172624,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"71d27a34ce5631c373cdf07044c98737267e55fe","tid":569931,"uid":172624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T07:18:43.000Z","msg":"Hi你元朗圖書館自修室個冷氣整咗勁耐都未整好<br />\n<br />\n前排得幾度個陣焗到出汗<br />\n係就係暖 但係焗到冇氣抖 勁焗 呼吸都辛苦 要行出去抖氣<br />\n而家仲要有流感 冷氣壞咗 空氣又唔流通 <br />\n晏d有一個人有流感or感冒就好易傳到成個自修室都係<br />\n元朗DSE考生就咁被收皮了<br />\n<br />\n焗到咁都唔知點專心去溫書 <br />\n<br />\n政府效率真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"430481e4ba606063fafcbac62d0e07b30370f15d","tid":569931,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T07:29:03.000Z","msg":"好撚臭 成浸阿婆味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2edb8f3ed24246914af8c237e6616f150dee81a9","tid":569931,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T07:30:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5fc2d8d6055741028435a501f260239c0912df7d","tid":569931,"uid":8033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T07:33:26.000Z","msg":"謝謝您透過「1823政府熱線」，表達對元朗公共圖書館自修室冷氣不足的意見。請於辦公時間內致電2479 2511與元朗公共圖書館助理館長黃小姐聯絡。 <br />\n<br />\n如希望我們致電給您，您亦可以電郵告訴我們您的電話號碼。 <br />\n<br />\n謝謝您使用我們的圖書館服務。 <br />\n<br />\n元朗公共圖書館<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f67d4a0ddaeaf36b4ab47db88853adf9ddcfe267","tid":569931,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T07:51:24.000Z","msg":"新館都壞 用咩貨"},{"pid":"1ec3abbdb36cfe8512ff80db621963440db9b999","tid":569931,"uid":172624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f67d4a0ddaeaf36b4ab47db88853adf9ddcfe267","tid":569931,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T07:51:24.000Z","msg":"新館都壞 用咩貨"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T08:02:07.0